title: Provoserer med T-skjortestunt
cleaned_sentences: Volodyymyr Zelenskyj Provokes with t-shirt stunt "Make Russia Small Again" became too much for the Russians.
Ukraine President Volodymyr Zelenskyj is wearing a new video on a t-shirt that does not go unnoticed in Russia.
"Make Russia Small Again," or "Do Russia Little Again," it says on the president's t-shirt in the video, which he has shared on Telegram.
The reference to Donald Trump's slogan "Make America Great Again" is not to be misunderstood.
Zelenskyj wants to shrink Russia by freeing the illegally annexed and occupied areas.
The president received the t-shirt by Ukrainian politician Hanna Hopko this week, writes The New Voice of Ukraine newspaper.
Russia responds by calling Zelenskyj an idiot, or "Bloody Jerk".
As the Kyiv Kingdom (Slavic State in the Middle Ages, journ.anm).
You said it yourself, your stupid idiot, writes Maria Zakharova, spokesperson for Russia's Foreign Ministry, at X.
